{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"local-name","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/local-name","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>local-name</code> 関数は、与えられたノード集合内の最初のノードのローカル名 (local name) を表す文字列を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">local-name( [<em>node-set</em>] )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"node-set\"><code><em>node-set</em></code> (省略可)</dt>\n <dd>このノード集合内の最初のノードのローカル名が返されます。引数を省略すると、現在のコンテキストノードが使用されます。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>文字列。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>ローカル名は展開名 (<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#dt-expanded-name\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">expanded-name</a>) のローカル部分です。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"定義","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-local-name\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.1</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko での対応","isH3":true,"content":"<p>対応済み。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"local-name 関数は、与えられたノード集合内の最初のノードのローカル名 (local name) を表す文字列を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"local-name","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"local-name","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"local-name","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"local-name","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/xpath/functions/local-name","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/xpath/functions/local-name/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/local-name","title":"local-name"}],"pageTitle":"local-name - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}